  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/28359f4d2068f2ad27eb229007d4cc26.avif?t=1730728840\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Protect the dinosaur eggs from an asteroid rain and save the world in TRex Hero. TRex Hero is a hilarious action game where you will have to literally run from one side to the other of the screen to save your life, while rescuing future generations of dinosaurs. Avoid the funny effects caused by asteroids, like freezing you, burning your tail, electrocuting you, or even making you throw up, while taking advantage of power-ups like your pterodactyl shield buddy, your powerful dash, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/90c931a2217691ee833b3707991e1f2d.poster.avif?t=1730728840\" width=154 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/90c931a2217691ee833b3707991e1f2d.webm?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/c2e7778f0a680c2283a9a9a93eec9874.poster.avif?t=1730728840\" width=154 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/c2e7778f0a680c2283a9a9a93eec9874.webm?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/3b1cb112a1658b22815754c2a17e23f5.poster.avif?t=1730728840\" width=154 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/3b1cb112a1658b22815754c2a17e23f5.webm?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/ef99f98b7fb36a140c0b2c0233950418.poster.avif?t=1730728840\" width=154 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/ef99f98b7fb36a140c0b2c0233950418.webm?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free In-Game Store</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/c6042c1d8ce40b8a27ec92c4c232d1e8.poster.avif?t=1730728840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/c6042c1d8ce40b8a27ec92c4c232d1e8.webm?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037560/extras/c6042c1d8ce40b8a27ec92c4c232d1e8.mp4?t=1730728840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use the Golden Eggs you earn during gameplay to buy additional skins and accessories!",
